trans-unit.source: Iterates over all preceding sibling content nodes in document order.
trans-unit.target: Itera em todos os nós de conteúdo irmãos anteriores na ordem do documento.

trans-unit.source: The state of the navigator changes only if the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingDocOrderIterator.MoveNext%2A> method has returned `true`.
trans-unit.target: O estado do se navegador alterações somente o <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingDocOrderIterator.MoveNext%2A> método retornou `true`.

trans-unit.source: The node from which you start traversing the nodes.
trans-unit.target: O nó do qual você começa o cruzamento dos nós.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the <see cref="T:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XmlNavigatorFilter" /> class, which enables you to filter nodes based on the name.
trans-unit.target: Uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XmlNavigatorFilter" />, que permite filtrar nós com base no nome.
Retorna o navegador de resultados atual.

trans-unit.source: The state of the navigator changes only if the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingDocOrderIterator.MoveNext%2A> method has returned `true`.
trans-unit.target: O estado do se navegador alterações somente o <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingDocOrderIterator.MoveNext%2A> método retornou `true`.

trans-unit.source: Positions the iterator on the next preceding sibling node.
trans-unit.target: Posiciona o iterador no próximo nó irmão anterior.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the next preceding sibling node exists; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o próximo nó irmão anterior existir; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: If the next preceding node exists, the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingDocOrderIterator.MoveNext%2A> method sets the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingDocOrderIterator.Current%2A> property to the current result navigator; otherwise, the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingDocOrderIterator.Current%2A> property remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: Se o próximo nó anterior existir, o <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingDocOrderIterator.MoveNext%2A> método define o <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingDocOrderIterator.Current%2A> propriedade para o navegador de resultados atual; caso contrário, o <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingDocOrderIterator.Current%2A> propriedade permanece inalterada.
